疑似炒鞋者，那么店家会拒绝发货。在线下，公司还采取了身份证核实的方式。「虽然不能完全杜绝炒鞋行为，但公司希望能尽量给消费者提供一个公平的消费环境。」（证券日报）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-852b1fc05c644f759f46e74f55044197_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "461 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454729245"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4eSayralqa4oEAMaCDYzMzMwNzExIJnY3oMGMAk4rQJACHIJNDU0NzI5MjQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1618477625.1081808", "card_id": "Q_28850652", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 323}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《我的叔叔于勒》里为什么说吃牡蛎非常优雅高贵?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "原文：「父亲被这种高贵的吃法打动了」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-515f89b180b2702078f40df6818e123a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "425 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/28850652"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I4eSayralqa4oEAMaBzM3MjMyNDAgxNWjqAUwGDicEEAJcggyODg1MDY1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1618477625.1086283", "card_id": "Q_454638451", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 194}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么看待漫画《进击的巨人》最终卷突然宣布加页？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "以下是机器翻译后的内容： 「最终回因为有很多想要描绘的东西，所以从平时的 45 页开始增加了，但是谏山先生说单行本中还有更多想要描绘的东西。」 这个加页的决定究竟是早有预谋的，还是说是因为看到最终话的风评后临时决定的？加页的内容有可能是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-6e0d3fb518af0b2b44ca973df6d6e017_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "419 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454638451"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI4eSayralqa4oEAMaCDYzMzEwNDcwIJO524MGMB445QZACnIJNDU0NjM4NDUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1618477625.1091287", "c